styleCard.description: An evocative cinematic folk piece that paints a picture of a scenic road trip through the breathtaking landscapes of New Zealand, from Queenstown's winding roads to the tranquil beauty of Te Anau. The music captures the essence of open vistas, quiet contemplation, and the steady progression of a memorable journey.

directions: Start at Gorge Road, Queenstown, Otago, 9300
Turn left to stay on Gorge Road
Take the exit on the left to Hallenstein Street toward Frankton
Turn left to stay on Hallenstein Street
Make a sharp right on Dublin Street
At the roundabout, take the third exit onto 6 toward Hospital / Remarkables / Ski Area / Invercargill / Milford Sound
At the roundabout, take the second exit to stay on Kawarau Road (6)
Turn left on Orbell Crescent, then turn right on Takahe Lane
Finish at 40 Sandy Brown Road, Te Anau, Southland, 9679, on the right
